data.description: Great opportunity to own a piece of paradise in Stratford Place! This three-bedroom, 2.5 bath first floor lakeview home features a one-car garage perfect for a vehicle or storage. With high ceilings and a split-floor plan upstairs bedrooms, this property has an open concept, allowing for tons of natural light and is great for entertaining. Tile throughout the home, new roofs and new water heater. Enjoy relaxing on the screened lanai with lake view. A prime location, Stratford Place is conveniently located just west of Interstate 75 off Pine Ridge Road and Whippoorwill Lane, only minutes from first-class shopping, dining, beaches and schools. Beaches are 15-20 minutes away or less.
